{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"1. (பாவிகளின் உயிர்களைப்) பலமாகப் பறிப்பவர்கள் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nāziʿāti gharqan ","translations":["By those who extract","violently","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nāziʿāti","gharqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2900],[2,2900,4515]]}},{"name":"79:2","price":"2. (நல்லவர்களின் ஆத்மாவை) எளிதாகக் கைப்பற்றுபவர்கள் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nāshiṭāti nashṭan ","translations":["And those who draw out","gently","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nāshiṭāti","nashṭan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2940],[2,2940,4305]]}},{"name":"79:3","price":"3. (ஆகாயத்திலும், கடலிலும்) அதிவேகமாக(ப் பறந்து) நீந்திச் செல்லும் வானவர்கள் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-sābiḥāti sabḥan ","translations":["And those who glide","swimming","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-sābiḥāti","sabḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,3195]]}},{"name":"79:4","price":"4. (இறைவனின் கட்டளையை நிறைவேற்ற) போட்டி போட்டுக்கொண்டு முந்தி செல்பவர்கள் மீதும் சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-sābiqāti sabqan ","translations":["And those who race each other","(in) a race","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-sābiqāti","sabqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1730],[2,1730,3195]]}},{"name":"79:5","price":"5. எல்லாக் காரியங்களையும் (இறைவனின் கட்டளைப்படி) நிர்வகிக்கின்ற (வான)வர்கள் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mudabirāti amran ","translations":["And those who arrange","(the) matter","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mudabirāti","amran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1970],[2,1970,3335]]}},{"name":"79:6","price":"6. (கொடிய பூகம்பத்தால் பூமி) பலமாக அதிர்ச்சியுறும் நாளில்,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma tarjufu al-rājifatu ","translations":["(The) Day","will quake","the quaking one","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","tarjufu","al-rājifatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,1640],[3,1640,3285]]}},{"name":"79:7","price":"7. (மேலும்) அதைத் தொடர்ந்து (பல பூகம்ப அதிர்ச்சிகள்) வரும் (நாளில் உலகம் முடிவுற்றே தீரும்).","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"tatbaʿuhā al-rādifatu ","translations":["Follows it","the subsequent","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["tatbaʿuhā","al-rādifatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2905]]}},{"name":"79:8","price":"8. அந்நாளில், உள்ளங்களெல்லாம் திடுக்கிட்டு நடுங்கிக் கொண்டிருக்கும்.","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qulūbun yawma-idhin wājifatun ","translations":["Hearts","that Day","will palpitate","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["qulūbun","yawma-idhin","wājifatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,3980],[3,3980,5425]]}},{"name":"79:9","price":"9. பார்வைகளெல்லாம் (பயத்தால்) கீழ்நோக்கி நிற்கும்.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"abṣāruhā khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Their eyes","humbled","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["abṣāruhā","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1490],[2,1490,2935]]}},{"name":"79:10","price":"10. (இவ்வாறிருக்க, நிராகரிப்பவர்கள் இதை மறுத்து) ‘‘நாம் (இறந்த பின்னர்) மெய்யாகவே நாம் (உயிர்ப்பிக்கப்பட்டு) முந்திய நிலைமைக்குத் திருப்பப்படுவோமா?''","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yaqūlūna a-innā lamardūdūna fī al-ḥāfirati ","translations":["They say","Will we","indeed be returned","to","the former state","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["yaqūlūna","a-innā","lamardūdūna","fī","al-ḥāfirati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,3290],[3,3290,4990],[4,4990,5230],[5,5230,7095]]}},{"name":"79:11","price":"11. (அதுவும்) நாம் உக்கி எலும்பாகப் போனதன் பின்னரா (உயிர் கொடுத்து எழுப்பப்படுவோம்?) என்று கூறுகின்றனர்.","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"a-idhā kunnā ʿiẓāman nakhiratan ","translations":["What! When","we are","bones","decayed","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["a-idhā","kunnā","ʿiẓāman","nakhiratan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,2650],[3,2650,3590],[4,3590,5955]]}},{"name":"79:12","price":"12. ‘‘அவ்வாறாயின், அது பெரும் நஷ்டமான மீட்சிதான் என்றும் அவர்கள் (பரிகாசமாகக்)'' கூறுகின்றனர்.","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qālū til'ka idhan karratun khāsiratun ","translations":["They say","This","then","(would be) a return","losing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["qālū","til'ka","idhan","karratun","khāsiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1520],[3,1520,2770],[4,2770,3870],[5,3870,5595]]}},{"name":"79:13","price":"13. (இது அவர்களுக்கு அசாத்தியமாகத் தோன்றலாம்; எனினும், நமக்கோ) அது ஓர் அதட்டல் (ஒரு உறுத்தல், ஒரு சப்தம்)தான்.","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-innamā hiya zajratun wāḥidatun ","translations":["Then only","it","(will be) a shout","single","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-innamā","hiya","zajratun","wāḥidatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2210],[2,2210,2630],[3,2630,4420],[4,4420,5915]]}},{"name":"79:14","price":"14. உடனே அவர்கள் அனைவரும் (உயிர் பெற்றெழுந்து) வந்து ஒரு திடலில் கூடிவிடுவார்கள்.","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā hum bil-sāhirati ","translations":["And behold","They","(will be) awakened","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","hum","bil-sāhirati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,2230],[3,2230,4255]]}},{"name":"79:15","price":"15. (நபியே!) மூஸாவுடைய செய்தி உமக்கு எட்டியதா?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu mūsā ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) story","(of) Musa","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","mūsā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1320],[3,1320,2250],[4,2250,3285]]}},{"name":"79:16","price":"16. ‘துவா' என்னும் பரிசுத்தமான ஓடைக்கு அவருடைய இறைவன் அவரை அழைத்ததை நினைவு கூறுங்கள்.","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idh nādāhu rabbuhu bil-wādi al-muqadasi ṭuwan ","translations":["When","called him","his Lord","in the valley","the sacred","(of) Tuwa","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","nādāhu","rabbuhu","bil-wādi","al-muqadasi","ṭuwan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,390],[2,390,1520],[3,1520,2520],[4,2520,3680],[5,3680,5020],[6,5020,6145]]}},{"name":"79:17","price":"17. ‘‘ஃபிர்அவ்னிடம் செல்வீராக! நிச்சயமாக அவன் வரம்பு மீறிவிட்டான்.","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idh'hab ilā fir'ʿawna innahu ṭaghā ","translations":["Go","to","Firaun","Indeed, he","(has) transgressed","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["idh'hab","ilā","fir'ʿawna","innahu","ṭaghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1470],[3,1470,2540],[4,2540,4330],[5,4330,5645]]}},{"name":"79:18","price":"18. (அவனிடம்) கூறுவீராக! ‘‘(பாவங்களை விட்டும்) நீ பரிசுத்தவானாக ஆக உனக்கு விருப்பம் தானா?","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faqul hal laka ilā an tazakkā ","translations":["And say","Would","[for] you","[to]","[that]","purify yourself","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["faqul","hal","laka","ilā","an","tazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,1100],[3,1100,1480],[4,1480,3780],[5,3780,4740],[6,4740,6005]]}},{"name":"79:19","price":"19. (அவ்வாறாயின்) உன் இறைவன் பக்கம் செல்லக்கூடிய வழியை நான் உனக்கு அறிவிக்கிறேன். அவனுக்கு நீ பயந்துகொள்'' (இவ்வாறு, மூஸாவுக்கு இறைவன் கட்டளையிட்டான்).","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ahdiyaka ilā rabbika fatakhshā ","translations":["And I will guide you","to","your Lord","so you would fear","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ahdiyaka","ilā","rabbika","fatakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1260],[2,1260,1780],[3,1780,2770],[4,2770,4025]]}},{"name":"79:20","price":"20. (மூஸா அவனிடம் சென்று அவ்வாறு கூறிப்) பெரியதொரு அத்தாட்சியையும் அவனுக்குக் காண்பித்தார்.","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-arāhu al-āyata al-kub'rā ","translations":["Then he showed him","the sign","the great","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-arāhu","al-āyata","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2170],[3,2170,3665]]}},{"name":"79:21","price":"21. (எனினும்) அவனோ, அதைப் பொய்யாக்கி (அவர் கூறியதற்கு) மாறு செய்தான்.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fakadhaba waʿaṣā ","translations":["But he denied","and disobeyed","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fakadhaba","waʿaṣā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2115]]}},{"name":"79:22","price":"22. பின்னர் (அவரை விட்டும்) விலகி (அவருக்குத் தீங்கிழைக்கவும்) முயற்சி செய்தான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma adbara yasʿā ","translations":["Then","he turned his back","striving","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","adbara","yasʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2240],[3,2240,3155]]}},{"name":"79:23","price":"23. இதற்காக(த் தன் மக்களை) ஒன்று கூட்டி (அவர்களுக்கு) அறிக்கையிட்டான்.","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faḥashara fanādā ","translations":["And he gathered","and called out","(23)"],"t